    "AI regression techniques, based on existing experimental or simulation results, can establish correlations between input parameters and material properties, reducing the time and economic waste associated with trial-and-error designs.",
    "Component tribologyThe basic components of tribology are the components that contain the Urelement of tribology system and undertake the key tribological functions of mechanical system, mainly including bearings, gears, tires, fasteners, and seals.",
